<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>체스 게임</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/chessGameStyle.css">
</head>

<body>

<h1 id="title"> Chess Game</h1>
<div class="right">
    <form action="/game/{{gameId}}/start" method="post">
        <button>시작</button>
    </form>

    <form action="/game/{{gameId}}/end" method="post">
        <button>종료</button>
    </form>

    <form action="/game/{{gameId}}/status" method="get">
        <button>점수</button>
    </form>

    <form action="/" method="get">
        <button>메인으로 돌아가기</button>
    </form>

    <br/><br/>

    <form action="/game/{{gameId}}/move" method="post">
        움직일 말의 위치와 움직일 위치를 입력하고 이동 버튼을 눌러주세요.
        <table class="move">
            <tr>
                <td>움직일 말의 위치</td>
                <td><input type="text" name="from"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>움직일 위치</td>
                <td><input type="text" name="to"></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <input type="submit" value="이동">
    </form>

    <br/><br/>

    <div class="score">
        {{#each score}}
            {{@key}} : {{this}} <br/>
        {{/each}}
    </div>

</div>

